	('8ada99c1483e50c901483fcdee270385', '各手册及说明文档下载', '<p style="line-height: 16px;">各手册及说明文档下载</p><hr/><p style="line-height: 16px;"><img style="vertical-align: middle; margin-right: 2px;" src="http://www.namkwong.org:8080/public/ueditor/dialogs/attachment/fileTypeImages/icon_pdf.gif"/><a style="font-size:12px; color:#0066cc;" href="/ueditor/jsp/upload/file/20140904/1409819678696085827.pdf" title="太湖世界文化论坛参展商手册0812.pdf">太湖世界文化论坛参展商手册0812.pdf</a></p><p style="line-height: 16px;"><img style="vertical-align: middle; margin-right: 2px;" src="http://www.namkwong.org:8080/public/ueditor/dialogs/attachment/fileTypeImages/icon_pdf.gif"/><a style="font-size:12px; color:#0066cc;" href="/ueditor/jsp/upload/file/20140904/1409826864300094050.pdf" title="招商表.pdf">招商表.pdf</a></p><p style="line-height: 16px;"><img style="vertical-align: middle; margin-right: 2px;" src="http://www.namkwong.org:8080/public/ueditor/dialogs/attachment/fileTypeImages/icon_pdf.gif"/><a style="font-size:12px; color:#0066cc;" href="/ueditor/jsp/upload/file/20140904/1409826864276092798.pdf" title="中医药文化发展高级别（澳门）会议暨中国道地中医药产品展览会邀请函.pdf">中医药文化发展高级别（澳门）会议暨中国道地中医药产品展览会邀请函.pdf</a></p><p style="line-height: 16px;"><br/></p><p><br/></p>'),
	('8ada99c148402244014840421a8d024f', '了解用户类型 Learn about Types of user', '<p><strong>*</strong> 演讲嘉宾 speakers</p><p>收到「嘉宾邀请函」，受组委会邀请参加会议并在会上演讲的重要人士</p><p>Guests （speakers）who have received &quot;Invitation Letter&quot; and are invited by the organizing committee to deliver a speech in the conference</p><hr/><p><strong>*</strong> 参会嘉宾 guests</p><p>收到「嘉宾邀请函」，受组委会邀请参加会议的重要人士（包括VIP嘉宾、一般参会嘉宾）</p><p>Honorable figures who have received &quot;Invitation Letter&quot; and are invited by the organizing committee (VIP guests and attending guests )</p><p>注：一般参会嘉宾需缴纳会议费</p><p>Attending guests need to pay relevant meeting charges to attend the conference</p><hr/><p><strong>*</strong> 嘉宾随行人员 entourages</p><p>随嘉宾来澳参会人员（包括一般随行人员、嘉宾配偶）</p><p>Attend the conference with the speakers and VIP guests (include spouse and entourage)</p><hr/><p><strong>*</strong> 媒体 media</p><p>参与报道本次会议的专业媒体人士</p><p>Professionals from media</p><hr/><p><strong>*</strong> 参展商 exhibitors</p><p>参与“中国道地中医药产品展览会“的专业展览商</p><p>Exhibitors in Exhibition about Chinese Genuine Regional Medicine Products</p><hr/><p><strong>*</strong> 参会观众 audience</p><p>收到「观众邀请函」，受组委会邀请以观众身份参加会议的专业人士</p><p>Professionals who have received &quot;Invitation Letter&quot; and are invited by the organizing committee to attend the conference as audiences</p><p><br/></p>'),
	('8ada99c14840224401484042fd9b0254', '所需文件和信息清单 List of Documents and Information', '<p style="text-align:center"><span style="font-size:19px;font-family:黑体">参会人员会议注册所需电子版资料清单</span></p><p style="text-align:center"><strong><span style="font-size:19px;font-family:&#39;Cambria&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;">Soft Copy Documents for Conference Registration</span></strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p style="text-align:center"><span style="font-size:19px;font-family:黑体">发言嘉宾</span></p><p style="text-align:center"><strong><span style="font-size:19px">Speakers </span></strong></p><p style="text-indent:31px"><span style="font-family:宋体">发言嘉宾需在</span>2014<span style="font-family:宋体">年</span>9<span style="font-family:宋体">月</span>27<span style="font-family:宋体">日之前完成网上注册。您需要在网上注册系统中提交您的个人信息和发言材料。提交资料包括：</span></p><p class="MsoListParagraph" style="margin-left:9px">1．<span style="font-family:宋体">个人简介（</span>150<span style="font-family:宋体">字左右，包括职位、研究领域和学术著作）</span></p><p class="MsoListParagraph" style="margin-left:9px">2．<span style="font-family:宋体">发言概要（</span>400<span style="font-family:宋体">字左右）</span></p><p class="MsoListParagraph" style="margin-left:9px">3．<span style="font-family:宋体">需要在发言中展示的</span>PPT<span style="font-family:宋体">或其他视频资料</span></p><p class="MsoListParagraph" style="margin-left:9px">4．<span style="font-family:宋体">入澳证件扫描件（签发页）</span></p><p class="MsoListParagraph" style="margin-left:9px">5．<span style="font-size: 9px;font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;">&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family:宋体">证件照（格式为</span>JPEG<span style="font-family:宋体">，大小不超过</span>300KB<span style="font-family: 宋体">）</span></p><p>All speakers are encouraged to<strong> </strong><span style=";color:#333333;border:none windowtext 1px;padding:0">complete online registration</span><span style=";color:#333333">&nbsp;before <strong>September 27, 2014</strong>. </span><span style="border: 1px none windowtext;padding: 0">You could submit your personal information together with speech documents through the online registration system</span><span style=";color:#333333;border:none windowtext 1px;padding:0">.</span><span style=";color:#333333">&nbsp;The documents including:</span></p><p>1.&nbsp;<span style="border: 1px none windowtext;padding: 0">A short biography (around 150 words, including Position, Research Field and Publications)</span></p><p>2.&nbsp;<span style="border: 1px none windowtext;padding: 0">An abstract of your speech (around 400 words)</span></p><p>3.&nbsp;<span style="border: 1px none windowtext;padding: 0">PPT and/or Video Demo which you want to present during your speech</span></p><p>4.&nbsp;<span style="border: 1px none windowtext;padding: 0">Scan copy of a valid passport (pages for visa)</span></p><p>5.&nbsp;<span style="border: 1px none windowtext;padding: 0">ID photo (JPEG format less than 300Kb) </span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p style="text-align:center"><span style="font-size:19px;font-family:黑体">参会嘉宾、特邀媒体、注册媒体、参展商、配偶、随行人员</span></p><p style="text-align:center"><strong><span style="font-size:19px">Guests, Invited Media, Registered Media, Exhibitors, Spouses, Entourages</span></strong></p><p>1.&nbsp;<span style="font-family:宋体">入澳证件扫描件（签发页）</span></p><p>2.&nbsp;<span style="font-family:宋体">证件照（格式为</span>JPEG<span style="font-family: 宋体">，大小不超过</span>300KB<span style="font-family:宋体">）</span></p><p>1.&nbsp;<span style="border: 1px none windowtext;padding: 0">Scan copy of a valid passport (pages for visa)</span></p><p>2.&nbsp;<span style="border: 1px none windowtext;padding: 0">ID photo (JPEG format less than 300Kb) </span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p style="text-align:center"><span style="font-size:19px;font-family:黑体">工作人员、志愿者、供应商</span></p><p style="text-align:center"><strong><span style="font-size:19px">Staff, Volunteers, Suppliers</span></strong></p><p>1.&nbsp;<span style="font-family:宋体">入澳证件扫描件（签发页）</span></p><p>2.&nbsp;<span style="font-family:宋体">证件照（格式为</span>JPEG<span style="font-family: 宋体">，大小不超过</span>300KB<span style="font-family:宋体">）</span></p><p>1.&nbsp;<span style="border: 1px none windowtext;padding: 0">Scan copy of a valid passport (pages for visa)</span></p><p>2.&nbsp;<span style="border: 1px none windowtext;padding: 0">ID photo (JPEG format less than 300Kb) </span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p style="text-align:center"><span style="font-size:19px;font-family:黑体">参会观众</span></p><p style="text-align:center"><strong><span style="font-size:19px">Audience </span></strong></p><p>1.&nbsp;<span style="font-family:宋体">个人有效身份证件扫描件</span></p><p>1.&nbsp;<span style="border: 1px none windowtext;padding: 0">Scan copy of valid </span><span style="border: 1px none windowtext;padding: 0">ID</span><span style="border: 1px none windowtext;padding: 0"> document</span></p><p><br/></p>'),
	('8ada99c14840224401484043c5fc025e', '浏览器要求 Browser Requirements', '<p>1.必须启用JavaScript</p><p>2.Internet Explorer版本10.0和更高版本，Mozilla Firefox或2.0或更高版本，Chrome16版本或更高版本,360安全浏览器。</p><p>&nbsp;</p><hr/><p>&nbsp;</p><p>1.JavaScript must be enabled</p><p>2.Internet Explorer version 10.0 and higher, Mozilla Firefox version 2.0 or higher, or Chrome version 16 or higher，360 secure browser.</p><p><br/></p>'),
	('8ada99c148402244014840443709025f', '如何完成注册 How to Complete the Registration', '<p>关于注册：</p><p>1. 注册前请您准备好以下资料：电子证件照、个人身份证件扫描件、入澳证件扫描件，如果您将作为演讲嘉宾出席本次会议，请准备中英文版个人简介各一份（100字左右）、发言内容提要、发言ppt。当您准备好以上资料，请点击 “注册入口”链接，开始进行会议注册。</p><p>2. 特别提示：您在注册时所使用的邮箱将作为今后会议互动平台的登录名，请您熟记。如果您需要多次操作完成整个注册过程，请您在每次登录前输入该邮箱，以便继续完成上次注册。</p><p>3. 如果您在注册过程中，忘记了您的登录密码，请在登录页点击“找回密码”链接，重新获取一个系统随机生成的密码。使用该密码登录后，通过“重置密码”设置新密码。</p><p>4. 如果在注册中遇到疑问，请依照页面上的填写说明完成信息填写。带有“*”的字段为必填选项。在没有完成必填项目填写时，注册信息将无法进行提交保存。</p><p>5. 注册系统将自动检查所输入的信息。在提交保存时，如果出现错误提示，请点击“上一步”或“下一步”按钮，重新阅读帮助信息并按照说明进行补填，完成填写后再次提交保存。</p><p>6，注册基本信息完成后，您还需要填写参会需求信息。两部分信息全部完成后，系统将把您所输入的信息梳理完整并请您再次检查信息的准确性。如果发现误填信息，可重新登录进行修改。</p><p>7. 请尽可能提前准备好所需资料，以便最短时间完成注册。</p><p>特别提示：</p><p>•请根据自身参会情况选择相应的参会注册人员类型进行注册；</p><p>•请注意上传照片及证件扫描件的格式及大小;</p><p>•嘉宾配偶和随行人员需进行单独注册;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>如果你停止注册工作超过3个小时或以上时间，您的本次注册操作将被系统判定为超时操作。请您在注册过程中适时保存所填写内容以避免不必要的重复操作。</p><p><br/></p><hr/><p><br/></p><p>About registration:</p><p>1. Before register, please prepare following materials: soft copy of your identity photo; scan copy of your ID document; scan copy of travel document for entry into Macau. If you are invited as speakers in the conference, please also prepare Chinese and English version of your personal introduction (about 100 words each), speech abstract and powerpoint. Then you may start to register.</p><p>2. Special notice: please remember the email used for register, it will be used as the login name. If you need several operations to finish the registration process, you may have to enter that email every time.</p><p>3. If you forget your login password, please click “find my password”. Then you will get a random <span style="font-size:16px;font-family: 宋体">password</span>, you may set up a new password after login in.</p><p>4. If you have any doubts in finish your information, you may enter according to notes. All “*” information need to be finished. You may not safe your information after all needed blanks are finished.</p><p>5. Register system will automatically check all the information, and will notice you if there is any error. You can click “<span style="font-size:16px;font-family: 宋体">previous&nbsp;step</span>” or “next step” to correct your information according to notes. After finishing all the blanks, you can safe your information.</p><p>6. After registering basic information, you also have to enter conference information. after finishing these two parts, the system will check and organize your information; if any error shows up, you may correct them according to notes.</p><p>7. Please prepare all needed materials as soon as possible in order to finish your registration.</p><p>Note:</p><p>In register, please choose types of participants according to your situation;</p><p>Please pay attention to the format and size of your photo and scan copy of documents;</p><p>Spouse and entourage need to register separately;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>If you stop to register over three hours, your registration will be regarded as overtime to connect to server, please save your information as long as you enter information in case of unnecessary repetition.</p><p><br/></p>'),
	('8ada99c1484022440148408ceb1204bd', '会议日程信息/Breif Agenda', '<p style="line-height: 16px;"><img style="vertical-align: middle; margin-right: 2px;" src="http://www.namkwong.org/public/ueditor/dialogs/attachment/fileTypeImages/icon_doc.gif"/><a style="font-size:12px; color:#0066cc;" href="/ueditor/jsp/upload/file/20140912/1410482491369025975.doc" title="会议简版日程.doc">会议简版日程.doc</a></p><p style="line-height: 16px;"><img style="vertical-align: middle; margin-right: 2px;" src="http://www.namkwong.org/public/ueditor/dialogs/attachment/fileTypeImages/icon_doc.gif"/><a style="font-size:12px; color:#0066cc;" href="/ueditor/jsp/upload/file/20140912/1410482491372014112.docx" title="Breif Agenda.docx">Breif Agenda.docx</a></p><p><br/></p>'),
	('8ada99c148417d6b014841bbe9e50199', 'Regulation of Macau Immigration', '<p>&nbsp; &nbsp;Guests who attend the meeting in Macau must hold valid passport or other travel document with visa.&nbsp;</p><p style="text-indent: 2em;"><strong style="text-indent: 2em;">“Visa” and “Entry permit “Exemption</strong></p><p style="text-indent: 2em;"><span style="text-indent: 0px;"> &nbsp;Nationals of the following countries are exempted in accordance with the written instruction of the Chief Executive.</span></p><p class="MsoListParagraph" style="margin-left:48px">1.<span style="font-size: 9px;font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>Holders of a passport issued by Andorra, Austria, Belgium, Bosnia and &nbsp;Herzegovina, Brazil, Britain(6 months), &nbsp;Bulgaria, &nbsp;Cape Verde, &nbsp;Croatia, Cyprus, Czech, &nbsp;Denmark, Dominica, Egypt, Estonia, Finland, &nbsp;France, Germany, Greece, Hungary, Iceland, &nbsp;Ireland, Israel, Italy, Japan, Latvia, Lebanon, &nbsp;Liechtenstein, Lithuania, Luxembourg, Macedonia, &nbsp;Mali, Mexico, Mongolia, Netherlands, Norway, &nbsp;Poland, Portugal, Romania Slovakia, Slovenia, &nbsp; South Korea, Spain, Sweden, Switzerland, &nbsp;Tanzania. will be granted Authorization to Stay for a maximum of 90 days upon arrival.</p><p class="MsoListParagraph" style="margin-left:48px">2.<span style="font-size: 9px;font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>Holders of a passport issued by Turkey, Canada, Indonesia, India, South Africa, U.S.A, Thailand, Uruguay, Namibia, Malaysia, Kiribati, Chile, Philippines, Seychelles, Singapore, New Zealand, Monaco, Australia, Samoa will be granted Authorization to Stay for a maximum of 30 days upon arrival;</p><p class="MsoListParagraph" style="margin-left:48px">3.<span style="font-size: 9px;font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>Holders of a Hong Kong Permanent Identity Card or a Re-entry Permit; holders of “Hong Kong Identity Card” must provide valid passport or travel document;</p><p class="MsoListParagraph" style="margin-left:48px">4.<span style="font-size: 9px;font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>Chinese in possession of a valid document for entering and departing from Macau;</p><p class="MsoListParagraph" style="margin-left:48px">5.<span style="font-size: 9px;font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>Holders of &quot;Diplomatic or consular identity card&quot; issued by the Macau Special Administrative Region or Hong Kong Special Administration Region;</p><p class="MsoListParagraph" style="margin-left:48px">6.<span style="font-size: 9px;font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>Holders of a diplomatic passport;</p><p class="MsoListParagraph" style="margin-left:48px">7.<span style="font-size: 9px;font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>Holders of a diplomatic passport, &quot;Laissez Passer&quot; issued by the United Nations;</p><p class="MsoListParagraph" style="margin-left:48px">8.<span style="font-size: 9px;font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>Non-Portuguese in possession of a travel document issued by the Portuguese authorities;</p><p class="MsoListParagraph" style="margin-left:48px">9.<span style="font-size: 9px;font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>Mainland residents who possess passport with (with a flight ticket to and entry visa of a third country or region will be granted to stay of a maximum of 7 days ( the destination must be China’s mainland and must entry mainland in a maximum of 7 days);</p><p class="MsoListParagraph" style="margin-left:48px">10.<span style="font-size: 9px;font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>Holders of passports issued by Taiwan will be granted Authorization to Stay for a maximum of 30 days upon arrival;&nbsp;</p><p style="margin-left: 24px; text-indent: 2em;"><strong>Regions Covered by The Individual Visit Scheme in China’s Mainland</strong>&nbsp;</p><p style="margin-left: 24px; text-indent: 2em;">Under the regulation of Ministry of Public Security of the People&#39;s Republic of China, the Individual Visit Scheme has been introduce to 49 Mainland cities, ie. residents with permanent household registration of the following 49 cities are allowed to visit Macau in their individual capacity. The Scheme is now implemented in 49 Mainland cities, including Beijing , Shanghai, Whole Guangdong province (all 21 cities), Tianjin,Chongqing, Nanjing, Suzhou, Wuxi (Jiangsu),Hangzhou, Ningbo, Taizhou (Zhejiang), Fuzhou (municipal district), Xiamen, Quanzhou (Fujian) ,Chengdu (Sichuan), Jinan (Shangdong), Dalian, Shenyang (Liaoning) ,Nanchang (Jiangxi),Changsha (Hunan), Nanning (Guangxi) ,Haikou (Hainan), Guiyang (Guizhou), Kunming (Yunnan), Shijiazhuang (Hebei), Zhengzhou (Henan), Changchun (Jilin), Hefei (Anhui) and Wuhan (Hubei)&nbsp;</p><p style="margin-left: 24px; text-indent: 2em;">Under the Scheme, guests who are from the above 49 cities with permanent household registration are eligible to apply for an Exit-entry Permit for travelling to and from Macau and an &quot;endorsement for individual visit (Geren Luyou)&quot; from the relevant Public Security Bureau Office. Guests whose permanent household registration are not included in the above 49 cities must apply for an Exit-entry Permit for travelling to and from Macau and an “endorsement for group visit” issued by the Public Security Bureau Office, and they may apply for checkpoint-passing service in Shenzhen or Zhuhai either individually or with the help of organizing committee upon their own will. For details of Exit-entry Permit and visit endorsement application, please visit the official website of Bureau of Exit and Entry Administration of the Ministry of Public Security at: <a href="http://www.mps.gov.cn/n16/n84147/n84211/n84273/n398922/index.html">http://www.mps.gov.cn/n16/n84147/n84211/n84273/n398922/index.html</a><span style="text-indent: 0px;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin-left: 24px; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="text-indent: 2em;">All guests who entered Macau are allowed to exit the checkpoint individually.</span></p><p><br/></p>'),
