	('077c09d447ddc0600147ddc121a50000', '太湖世界文化论坛2014年中医药文化发展高级别（澳门）会议', 'Agenda of the High-level Conference on the Development of Traditional Chinese Medicine Culture 2014 (Macau), World Cultural Forum (Taihu, China)', '2014/11/13 09:00', '2014/11/14 17:00', '澳门', NULL, 'uploadFiles/mettings/077c09d447ddc0600147ddc121a50000/bannerlogo.png;', 'tcf', '<p>\r\n				2014年11月12-14日，最权威、规格最高、规模最大、影响范围\r\n				最广的顶级世界传统医学与中医药文化交流盛会——太湖世界文化论坛2014年世界传统医学文化保护与发展高级别（澳门）会议暨中国道地中医药产品展览会将在中国澳门召开。\r\n				太湖世界文化论坛联合澳门最大的综合性企业南光（集团）有限公司秉承“积极推动中医药产业发展，将澳门打造成为中医药国际重要交流、贸易平台”的宗旨，聚合千名世界传统医学领域权威人士、\r\n				中医药企业领袖、行业精英、专家学者、主流传媒，以“创新、发展世界传统医学，推动澳门产业结构适度多元发展”为理念，力求通过新锐前瞻的思想碰撞，促进人类传统医学迈进崭新时代。\r\n				在此，我们诚邀与您携手共同拉开太湖世界文化论坛2014年世界传统医学文化保护与发展高级别（澳门）会议的大幕！</p><p>\r\n			</p><p>\r\n				为了更好地提供会期接待服务，诚请您选用网上注册形式完成参会报名。系统使用说明将在下方标明以便您可以轻松完成大会注册，请您关注。			</p><p>\r\n			</p><p>\r\n				再次感谢您对太湖世界文化论坛2014年世界传统医学文化保护与发展高级别（澳门）会议暨中国道地中医药产品展览会的支持，期待与您澳门相会！			</p>', '<p style="text-align: left; text-indent: 2em;">On November 12th to 14th, the High-level Conference on the Protection and Development of Global Traditional Medicine Culture 2014 (Macau) — Exhibition about Chinese Genuine Regional Medicine Products will be held in Macau, China. It is regarded as the most authoritative grand platform for the exchanges of global traditional medicine and traditional Chinese medicine (TCM), and will definitely leave widespread effects in the whole world. The conference is co-organized by World Cultural Forum (Taihu, China) and Nam Kwong (Group) Company Ltd., the largest comprehensive enterprise in Macau, with the aims of “promoting the development of TCM industry, and building Macau into an international platform for TCM exchanges and trades”. Based on the notion of “Innovating and developing global traditional medicine, advancing the diversified development of Macau industrial structure ”, the conference invited traditional medicine authorities, TCM business leaders, elites, scholars and professionals from mainstream media to share their sharp and forward-looking opinions, and jointly bringing traditional medicine into a brand new era. Here, we sincerely invite you to open the prelude of the High-level Conference on the Protection and Development of Global Traditional Medicine Culture 2014 (Macau).</p><p style="text-align: left; text-indent: 2em;">In order to better provide reception services during the conference, please enroll online and finish the registration. Guidelines are listed at the bottom to facilitate your register.&nbsp;</p><p style="text-align: left; text-indent: 2em;">Thank you again for supporting the High-level Conference on the Protection and Development of Global Traditional Medicine Culture 2014 (Macau) — Exhibition about Chinese Genuine Regional Medicine Products. We look forward to meet you in Macau!</p><p><br style="text-align: left;"/></p>', '1'),
